## KNOWN ENVIRONMENT NOTES

  D-04  Safari / macOS
        - SameSite=Lax cookie policy differs from Chromium; validate "Your Videos" scoping carefully
        - Test cookie persistence explicitly (TC-H06, TC-H07)

  D-02  Firefox / Windows 11
        - Enhanced Tracking Protection (ETP) may block or partition cookies by default
        - Disable ETP for the test domain or document behaviour difference

  M-02  iPhone 14 / Safari iOS
        - iOS WebKit enforces ITP (Intelligent Tracking Prevention) — cookies may expire in 7 days
        - Validate that UUID cookie survives a 24h gap between sessions

  M-01  Pixel 5 / Chrome Android
        - Portrait viewport is the default; validate responsive layout of form controls (selects, toggles)

  M-03  iPad / Safari iPadOS
        - Test in both Portrait (820x1180) and Landscape (1180x820) orientations
        - Focus: layout integrity of two-column generation settings panels
